WOMEN'S TENNIS 
</P>
<P>
Manuela Maleeva, 23, ranked eighth in the world in women's singles, has entered 
the Great American Bank tennis tournament to be played at the San Diego Tennis 
and Racquet Club Aug. 6-12. The field also includes top-ranked Steffi Graf and 
Wimbledon champ Martina Navratilova. 
</P>
