Tropical Ice Cream, 1236 W. 5th St., Santa Ana 
</P>
<P>
Dates Closed: May 15-16 
</P>
<P>
Reasons Cited for Suspension: Summary suspension: all plumbing fixtures missing 
from restrooms; no hot or cold water. 
</P>
