<P>
Pittson Co.: In an unusual move, Pittson Co. has elevated two executives in its 
Burlington Air Express subsidiary in Irvine to serve as joint chief executives 
of the international air freight firm. The move follows the promotion earlier 
this month of David L. Marshall, Burlington's chairman and chief executive 
since 1987, to the posts of vice chairman and chief financial officer of 
Connecticut-based Pittson. 
</P>
